properties.description: To get presentations data from Cadmium Rest API.

sqlReaderQuery.value:
SELECT
    'HarvesterJsonAPI.asp?APIKey=' + '@{variables('GetAPIKey')}' + '&Method=getPresentations&eID=' + CAST(Event_ID AS VARCHAR) AS Presentation_Url
FROM 
    admin.Event_Details WHERE IsActive = 1;

activities.name: Execute Get Cadmium API key Pipeline

pipeline.referenceName: GET Cadmium API Key from Key Vault

dependsOn.activity: Execute Get Cadmium API key Pipeline
